The '''Great Library of Manuals''' was located on the planet [[Te Hasa/Legends|Te Hasa]] within the [[Gree Enclave/Legends|Gree Enclave]] and served as the repository in which all [[Gree (species)/Legends|Gree]] knowledge as well as artifacts or devices were stored. This world was vital to the enclave ever since the Gree's slow decline and, as such, was maintained by twelve to fourteen [[Textmaster]]s. It was hoped that continued study of the technological relics would one day unlock their secrets to the Gree once again.<ref name="The Gree Enclave">{{JournalCite|8|The Gree Enclave}}</ref>

